OL,3,CWhat happens next with Greater
OL,4,CManchester mayoralty after Burnham's
OL,5,Cwin?
OL,7,FAndy Burnham's historic victory in the
OL,8,FMakerfield by-election sets off a
OL,9,Frapid chain reaction for both Greater
OL,10,FManchester and the wider UK political
OL,11,Flandscape.
OL,13,FA metro mayor cannot simultaneously
OL,14,Fserve as an MP, a clear legal and
OL,15,Felectoral process is now underway to
OL,16,Ffind someone new to take on the role.
OL,18,FHere is what happens next:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
