OL,3,CWhat happens next with Greater
OL,4,CManchester mayoralty after Burnham's
OL,5,Cwin?
OL,7,FAndy Burnham has won a seat as an MP -
OL,8,Fbut can he still be the Mayor of
OL,9,FGreater Manchester?
OL,11,FNo. Andy Burnham cannot be mayor and a
OL,12,Fmember of parliament. He had seven
OL,13,Fdays - from the moment of his election
OL,14,F- to resign from the post which he has
OL,15,Fheld for almost a decade.
OL,17,FHe handed in his resignation on 19
OL,18,FJune - triggering the process of the
OL,19,Fby-election.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
