OL,3,CWhat happens next with Greater
OL,4,CManchester mayoralty after Burnham's
OL,5,Cwin?
OL,7,FBurnham cannot do both jobs because
OL,8,Fthe Mayor of Greater Manchester holds
OL,9,FPolice and Crime Commissioner (PCC)
OL,10,Fpowers and UK law strictly dictates
OL,11,Fthat the office holder cannot
OL,12,Fsimultaneously serve as an MP.
OL,14,FNow that the MP is representing the
OL,15,FMakerfield constituency in the
OL,16,Fcaptial, he is legally disqualified
OL,17,Ffrom continuing as Mayor and must step
OL,18,Fdown to take his seat in Westminster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
