OL,3,CWhat happens next with Greater
OL,4,CManchester mayoralty after Burnham's
OL,5,Cwin?
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FWhen will a mayoral election take
OL,13,Fplace?
OL,15,FA mayoral by-election must take place
OL,16,Fwithin a maximum of 35 working days
OL,17,Fafter the office of mayor has been
OL,18,Fvacated. This means it would have to
OL,19,Fbe held by the 6 August 2026 at the
OL,20,Flatest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
