OL,3,CWhat happens next with Greater
OL,4,CManchester mayoralty after Burnham's
OL,5,Cwin?
OL,7,FA date of 30 July 2026 has now been
OL,8,Fset.
OL,10,FThe successful candidate in a mayoral
OL,11,Fby-election will hold office until the
OL,12,Fnext scheduled election for the
OL,13,Fmayoralty, in May 2028.
OL,15,FWho is in the running for the Greater
OL,16,FManchester mayoral election?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
