OL,3,CWhat happens next with Greater
OL,4,CManchester mayoralty after Burnham's
OL,5,Cwin?
OL,7,FPolitical parties will rushing their
OL,8,Fselection processes. No party has yet
OL,9,Fto confirm their candidate but it has
OL,10,Fbeen heavily tipped that Bev Craig,
OL,11,Fleader of Manchester City Council,
OL,12,Fwill be Labour's choice.
OL,14,FReform and Greens are likely to put up
OL,15,Fa candidate in the coming days.
OL,17,FWho will take over the position from
OL,18,Fnow until the next mayor is elected?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
