OL,3,CWhat happens next with Greater
OL,4,CManchester mayoralty after Burnham's
OL,5,Cwin?
OL,7,FTo prevent a power vacuum at the
OL,8,FGreater Manchester Combined Authority
OL,9,F(GMCA), an interim leader is required.
OL,11,FPaul Dennett - the Mayor of Salford
OL,12,Fand Burnham's Deputy Mayor - is
OL,13,Fexpected to step in as acting mayor to
OL,14,Foversee day-to-day operations and
OL,15,Fregional strategies until a permanent
OL,16,Fsuccessor is elected.
OL,18,FWhich voting system would be used in
OL,19,Fthe mayoral by-election?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
