OL,3,CWhat happens next with Greater
OL,4,CManchester mayoralty after Burnham's
OL,5,Cwin?
OL,7,FMillions of voters across all 10
OL,8,Fboroughs of Greater Manchester will be
OL,9,Feligible to cast a ballot.
OL,11,FCurrently, mayoral elections use the
OL,12,F'first-past-the-post' voting system.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
